## DEV COMMAND SHORTCUTS

Always prefer these established scripts. Do not invent alternative commands unless the user explicitly requests a change.

### Monorepo Root (`/`)

```bash
# Parallel API + Web dev servers
pnpm dev                    # API :3000 + Web :3001

# Individual services
pnpm dev:api                # NestJS watch mode
pnpm dev:web                # Next.js dev :3001

# Prisma automation (handles Studio/API lock release)
pnpm prisma:sync            # migrate deploy + generate + seed
pnpm prisma:sync:dev        # migrate dev + generate + seed
pnpm prisma:watch           # auto-sync on schema.prisma changes
pnpm prisma:studio          # GUI at http://localhost:5555

# QA pyramid
pnpm test:qa                # unit + API integration
pnpm test:qa:web            # Jest unit + Playwright E2E
pnpm test:qa:flutter        # Flutter widget + integration
pnpm test:smoke             # live API + web health (stack must be running)
pnpm test:qa:live           # smoke + API live e2e

# Build & quality
pnpm typecheck
pnpm lint
pnpm build
```

### Infrastructure

```bash
cd fleetflow-infra
docker compose up -d        # postgres + redis (+ optional API)
docker compose down         # preserves named volumes
docker compose down -v      # DESTROYS data — fresh start only
```

### API (`fleetflow-api/`)

```bash
pnpm start:dev              # NestJS watch
pnpm test:unit              # geo-matching, pricing specs
pnpm test:integration       # health, RBAC supertest
node test/run-live-e2e.mjs  # live stack e2e (requires running API)
```

### Web (`fleetflow-web/`)

```bash
pnpm dev                    # :3001
pnpm test                   # Jest unit
pnpm test:e2e               # Playwright headless
pnpm test:e2e:ui            # Playwright interactive
npx playwright install chromium   # first-time browser install
```

**Reusable UI:** `AppLink`, `ActionLoadingOverlay`, `Skeleton`, `PageSection` — see `fleetflow-web/docs/COMPONENTS.md`.

**Portal RBAC:** update `lib/auth/access.ts` + `middleware.ts` when adding routes — skill: `.cursor/skills/fleetflow-rbac-portal/SKILL.md`.

### Flutter (`fleetflow-app/`)

```bash
flutter pub get
flutter test test/widget
flutter test integration_test/app_test.dart
flutter run
```

